      <p>A framework here is a <strong>named way of describing a pattern</strong> we see over and over in real QuickBooks files &mdash; a diagnostic lens or a defined method, given a precise name so it can be talked about, taught, and scoped. They are <strong>coined concepts and methodologies, not statistics, surveys, or studies</strong>: each names a real dynamic or discipline, defined once, in plain language. Two describe what goes <em>wrong</em> when books are neglected; two describe how we do the work <em>right</em>.</p>
